# Our patched busytex engine (MIT, ~30 MB) IS committed — see LICENSE-busytex.
# The stock TeX Live filesystem bundles (~190 MB, mixed per-package licenses)
# are NOT committed; they're downloaded from the upstream busytex release at
# build time by scripts/download-tex-engine.sh. The small MIT glue
# (busytex_worker.js, busytex_pipeline.js) is committed too.
#
# So busytex.js + busytex.wasm are intentionally NOT ignored here.
*.data
texlive-basic.js
ubuntu-texlive-*.js
# Build-output copies + stock backups — not committed.
*.stock
busytex.patched.js
busytex.patched.wasm
